OL,4,G1115FThe Simpsons
OL,5,G1145FFour in a Bed
OL,6,     GOne pair in Portsmouth are wowed
OL,7,     Gby their room; another find the
OL,8,     Gdesign delightful. But a duvet
OL,9,     Gdisaster could spell the host's
OL,10,     Gdoom, while the parking is
OL,11,     Gutterly frightful. _WorldPoetryDay
OL,12,G1215FFour in a Bed
OL,13,     GThe breakfast in Bournemouth is
OL,14,     Gbrimming with quality. But sod
OL,15,     Gthe high calibre; the guests just
OL,16,     Gwant quantity. _WorldPoetryDay
