OL,4,G1250FFour in a Bed
OL,5,     GPaul and Tracey host in Dorset
OL,6,     Gand aim to impress, with their
OL,7,     Gfashionable hospitality. But
OL,8,     Gsubstandard sleep leaves one
OL,9,     Gguest depressed, and feedback
OL,10,     Gpresents abnormalities.
OL,11,     G_WorldPoetryDay
OL,12,G1320FFour in a Bed
OL,13,     GAt a scenic glampsite in
OL,14,     GCornwall, there are beautiful
OL,15,     Gvistas for all. But dusty
OL,16,     Gdiscoveries, leave some guests
OL,17,     Gall snuffly - could this be the
OL,18,     Ghosts' big downfall?
OL,19,     G_WorldPoetryDay
