OL,4,G1350FFour in a Bed
OL,5,     GFinger-pointing, rows and
OL,6,     Gvenomous jibes; no this isn't
OL,7,     GPrime Minister's Questions. It's
OL,8,     Gpayment day on Four in a Bed -
OL,9,     Gand there's plenty of feedback
OL,10,     Gfor digestion. _WorldPoetryDay
OL,11,G1420FKirstie and Phil's Love It or
OL,12,     FList It
OL,13,     GThere once was a fellow called
OL,14,     GPhil. He and Kirstie were rather
OL,15,     Gbrill. At loving or listing.
OL,16,     GUsing methods consisting. Of know-
OL,17,     Ghow and bargaining skill.
OL,18,     G_WorldPoetryDay
