OL,4,G1525FLocation, Location, Location
OL,5,     GThe search starts with a million-
OL,6,     Gpound budget. Finding the right
OL,7,     Gplace; can Kirstie nudge it? And
OL,8,     Gcompromise is put to the test,
OL,9,     Gwhen Rebecca and Sohail's kids
OL,10,     Gfly the nest. _WorldPoetryDay
OL,11,G1625FSleepless in Seattle
OL,12,     GClassic romcom; love in the Big
OL,13,     GApple. Long distance
OL,14,     Grelationships can be such a
OL,15,     Gbattle. Annie in Baltimore,
OL,16,     Galready spoken for, and Sam is
OL,17,     Gsleepless, up in Seattle.
OL,18,     G_WorldPoetryDay
