OL,5,     FColour
OL,6,     GEgypt takes control of its
OL,7,     Gtreasures, while experts race to
OL,8,     Gfind more. Extraordinary findings
OL,9,     Gare made at Tanis. But then the
OL,10,     Gworld goes to war. _WorldPoetryDay
OL,11,G2000FRoman Empire by Train with Alice
OL,12,     FRoberts
OL,13,     GIn Tarragona, Alice learns how
OL,14,     Gthe Romans gained control of the
OL,15,     Gentire Med. In Cartagena, she
OL,16,     Gmarvels at subterranean riches of
OL,17,     Gsilver and lead. _WorldPoetryDay
