OL,4,G2100FBill Bailey's Vietnam
OL,5,     GIn Hanoi, Bill explores Vietnam's
OL,6,     Gcomplex relationship with life,
OL,7,     Gdeath and war; a culture defined
OL,8,     Gby spirituality, femininity and a
OL,9,     Gunique tradition at its core.
